measurement.rubric:
You are evaluating whether an eBay deal analysis is accurate and trustworthy. You will receive: the listing details, the LLM's condition assessment, the market price reference used, and the calculated discount.
Score each criterion and return ONLY valid JSON — no prose.
{ "condition_verified": float 0.0-1.0, // how confident is the condition assessment? "discount_accuracy": float 0.0-1.0, // is the market price reference fair and apples-to-apples? "deal_actionability": float 0.0-1.0, // can the user actually act on this right now? "alert_precision": float 0.0-1.0, // based on prior user feedback, is this the type of deal they want? "composite": float 0.0-1.0, // weighted average "red_flags": [], // any concerns: vague description, low seller rating, parts-only risk, etc. "recommendation": "alert" | "skip" | "needs_more_info" }

stage.user:
Evaluate this eBay listing for "{item.query}" listed as "{item.condition}" condition.

LISTING TITLE: {listing.title}
LISTING DESCRIPTION: {listing.description}
ITEM SPECIFICS: {listing.item_specifics}
SELLER FEEDBACK SCORE: {listing.seller_feedback_pct}% ({listing.seller_feedback_count} ratings)
NUMBER OF PHOTOS: {listing.photos_count}
ASKING PRICE: ${listing.price} (+ ${listing.shipping_cost} shipping)

Assess the following and return JSON:
{{
  "is_functional": true | false | "uncertain",
  "condition_matches_claim": true | false | "uncertain",
  "red_flags": [list of strings — any concerning phrases or omissions],
  "parts_only_risk": float 0.0-1.0,
  "confidence": float 0.0-1.0,
  "condition_summary": string max 60 words,
  "pass": true | false   // true only if is_functional=true AND confidence >= 0.75
}}

ITEM: {item.query} ({item.condition})
LISTING PRICE: ${listing.price}
SHIPPING COST: ${listing.shipping_cost}
TOTAL COST TO BUYER: ${listing.total_cost}

MARKET PRICE (median of last 10 sold, same condition): ${market_price.median}
MARKET PRICE RANGE: ${market_price.p25} – ${market_price.p75}

CONDITION ASSESSMENT: {condition_check.condition_summary}
SELLER FEEDBACK: {listing.seller_feedback_pct}%
LISTING TYPE: {listing.buying_option}
TIME REMAINING: {listing.time_remaining}

PRIOR ALERTS FOR THIS CATEGORY: {prior_alerts}

Evaluate and return JSON:
{{
  "true_discount_pct": float,             // (market_median - total_cost) / market_median * 100
  "meets_50pct_threshold": true | false,
  "market_price_confidence": float 0.0-1.0, // how reliable is the market price reference?
  "deal_quality": "exceptional" | "good" | "marginal" | "skip",
  "actionability": "buy_now" | "watch" | "skip",
  "estimated_resale_value": float,         // if reselling: conservative market price
  "estimated_profit_after_fees": float,    // resale - cost - ebay_fees(13%) - shipping
  "one_line_summary": string max 80 chars
}}

alerts.format:
🛒 DEAL: {item.query}
💰 ${listing.price} vs ${market_price.median} market → {deal_evaluation.true_discount_pct}% off
⏱ {listing.time_remaining} remaining
📦 {condition_check.condition_summary}
💵 Est. profit after fees: ${deal_evaluation.estimated_profit_after_fees}
🔗 {listing.url}
